= Extracted Lists
<extracted-lists>
The list environments below are extracted from arXiv LaTeX source and
wrapped for pdfLaTeX validation.

+ The adjoint representation of \${\\cal G}\_0\$ decomposes into rank
  \$\\cal
  G\$ multiplets of the subalgebra \$\\cal S\$ ([su2]).

+ The representation of \${\\cal G}\_0\$ in \${\\cal G}\_1\$ also
  decomposes into rank \$\\cal G\$ \$\\cal S\$-multiplets.

+ After the gauge fixing there is a one to one correspondence between
  remaining currents and \$\\cal S\$-multiplets in the adjoint of
  \$\\cal G\$.

+ The number of remaining currents with integer and half integer height
  is the same and equal to the rank of \$\\cal G\$.

+ The conformal spin, w.r.t. $L\(x\)$, of the remaining current
  associated to the \$\\cal S\$-multiplet with highest weight $j$ is
  $\(j + 1\)$.
